  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>commercial & passenger cars</p></li><li><p>Handle customer enquiries and provide professional advice</p></li><li><p>Arrange test drives and follow up with customers</p></li><li><p>Prepare quotations and sales documentation</p></li><li><p>Achieve monthly sales targets</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Experience in vehicle sales is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Good communication and negotiation skills</p></li><li><p>Self-motivated and responsible</p></li><li><p>Valid Class 3 driving licence</p></li><li><p>Able to work weekends when required</p></li></ul><p><strong>Remuneration:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Basic salary + commission</p></li><li><p>Incentives & performance bonuses</p></li><li><p>Training provided</p></li></ul><p></p>",
